<P><PB N="90" REF="101">I mu&s;t harp a little more upon this &s;tring&mdash;Don't you ob&s;erve, how much your brother's influence has over-topp'd yours, &s;ince he has got into fortunes &s;o con&s;iderable; and &s;ince you have given &s;ome of them an appetite to <HI>continue</HI> in them&s;elves the po&s;&s;e&s;&s;ion of your e&s;tate, unle&s;s you comply with their terms?</P>
